snippet: A U.S. judge on Tuesday accepted the guilty plea of a former stockbroker to participating in an insider trading scheme, one week after expressing concern about whether the defendant's explanation of the crime was legally sufficient....

headline.print_headline: U.S. Judge Accepts Broker's Guilty Plea in IBM Insider Trading Case
headline.main: U.S. Judge Accepts Broker's Guilty Plea in IBM Insider Trading Case

lead_paragraph: A U.S. judge on Tuesday accepted the guilty plea of a former stockbroker to participating in an insider trading scheme, one week after expressing concern about whether the defendant's explanation of the crime was legally sufficient.
